24
00:02:27,320 --> 00:02:28,240
Don't worry about it.

25
00:02:28,600 --> 00:02:29,560
Do well in the exam.

26
00:02:29,840 --> 00:02:30,790
Don't mess up.

27
00:02:34,710 --> 00:02:35,350
Ms. Ling.

28
00:02:35,750 --> 00:02:36,350
I...

29
