Boss.

35
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,200
Ling.

36
00:03:09,790 --> 00:03:10,480
Haven't you left yet?

37
00:03:11,760 --> 00:03:13,480
I'll take out the trash and leave.

38
00:03:42,230 --> 00:03:43,400
